To build on linux

sudo add-apt-repository ppa:bitcoin/bitcoin
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install build-essential libtool autotools-dev autoconf pkg-config libssl-dev libevent-dev libboost-all-dev git libminiupnpc-dev automake libdb4.8-dev libdb4.8++-dev

If building the Linux Qt you must have the following deps as well.

sudo apt-get install libqt5gui5 libqt5core5a libqt5dbus5 qttools5-dev qttools5-dev-tools libprotobuf-dev protobuf-compiler libqrencode-dev

git clone https://github.com/white92d15b7/NLX.git

cd NLX
./autogen.sh
./configure
sudo make
sudo make install

nullexd or nullex-qt


